(35, 1, '2015-06-11 19:47:58', '2015-06-11 19:47:58', '<p class="txt-normal"><span class="b1">Interserve</span> ministry is deeply committed to the five core values that serve as the driving force behind our unrelenting pursuit of the vision.</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left" valign="top" width="36%"><span class="txt-normal"><img src="http://www.isvindia.org/about/values/images/values.gif" alt="Core Values" width="279" height="256" /></span></td>\r\n<td align="left" valign="top" width="64%"><span class="b1">INCLUSIVITY</span><span class="txt-normal">\r\nWe welcome a rich diversity of cultures, providing opportunity for growth and learning. We believe in gender inclusivity, women and men share ministry and leadership roles.</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="b1">INTEGRITY</span><span class="txt-normal">\r\nWe strive for excellence and integrity in every aspect of our lives.</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="b1">HUMILITY</span><span class="txt-normal">\r\nWe respect and accept each other and those whom we are called to serve. We do not seek recognition for ourselves or the name of Interserve.</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="b1">RELATIONSHIP</span><span class="txt-normal">\r\nWe are a family bound together by relationships of mutual accountability. Where there is breakdown of relationships, we pray and work for reconciliation.</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="b1">SERVICE</span><span class="txt-normal">\r\nOur call is to enable others to experience the Kingdom of God and live as disciples of Jesus Christ.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="txt-normal"></p>', 'Our Core Values', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'our-core-values', '', '', '2015-06-11 19:50:16', '2015-06-11 19:50:16', '', 17, 'http://local.wordpress.dev/?page_id=35', 3, 'page', '', 0),
