(50, 1, '2015-06-15 18:35:03', '2015-06-15 18:35:03', '<span class="b1"><strong>Interserve</strong></span><span class="txt-normal"> is committed to serve the underprivileged peoples of Asia and the Arab world – getting alongside them; uplifting them from their material, physical, mental and spiritual needs.</span>\r\n\r\nWe work in partnership with other agencies involved in varied professional arenas. Using our extensive network and expertise, we serve the Indian Christian community in practical ways by placing committed professionals in ministry opportunities within India and overseas (particularly the Arabian Gulf, Central and East Asia). Presently, we have over 50 Indian partners serving in more than 18 Indian states and three other countries. Each of them is involved in a unique ministry integrating their professional skills and the mandate of missions.', 'Our Work', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'our-work', '', '', '2015-06-15 18:36:21', '2015-06-15 18:36:21', '', 0, 'http://local.wordpress.dev/?page_id=50', 2, 'page', '', 0),
(51, 1, '2015-06-15 18:35:03', '2015-06-15 18:35:03', '<table border="0" width="72%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="6" bgcolor="#93BFF0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="39%"><a href="http://www.isvindia.org/work/seminars/index.html">• Envisioning &amp; Equipping Seminars</a></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="28%"><a href="http://www.isvindia.org/work/partner-org/index.html">• Partner Organizations</a></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="33%"><a href="http://www.isvindia.org/work/partner-churches/index.html">• Partner Churches</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" bgcolor="#E8EBFD"><a href="http://www.isvindia.org/work/orientation/index.html">• Cross cultural Orientation</a></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" bgcolor="#E8EBFD"><a href="http://www.isvindia.org/work/research/index.html">• Research</a></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" bgcolor="#E8EBFD"><a href="http://www.isvindia.org/work/education/index.html">• Educational Projects</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<span class="txt-normal"><strong>\r\n</strong></span><span class="b1"><strong>Interserve</strong></span><span class="txt-normal"> is committed to serve the underprivileged peoples of Asia and the Arab world – getting alongside them; uplifting them from their material, physical, mental and spiritual needs.\r\n\r\nWe work in partnership with other agencies involved in varied professional arenas. Using our extensive network and expertise, we serve the Indian Christian community in practical ways by placing committed professionals in ministry opportunities within India and overseas (particularly the Arabian Gulf, Central and East Asia). Presently, we have over 50 Indian partners serving in more than 18 Indian states and three other countries. Each of them is involved in a unique ministry integrating their professional skills and the mandate of missions.</span>', 'Our Work', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '50-re