(53, 1, '2015-06-15 18:36:21', '2015-06-15 18:36:21', '<span class="b1"><strong>Interserve</strong></span><span class="txt-normal"> is committed to serve the underprivileged peoples of Asia and the Arab world – getting alongside them; uplifting them from their material, physical, mental and spiritual needs.</span>\r\n\r\nWe work in partnership with other agencies involved in varied professional arenas. Using our extensive network and expertise, we serve the Indian Christian community in practical ways by placing committed professionals in ministry opportunities within India and overseas (particularly the Arabian Gulf, Central and East Asia). Presently, we have over 50 Indian partners serving in more than 18 Indian states and three other countries. Each of them is involved in a unique ministry integrating their professional skills and the mandate of missions.', 'Our Work', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '50-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-15 18:36:21', '2015-06-15 18:36:21', '', 50, 'http://local.wordpress.dev/2015/06/50-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(54, 1, '2015-06-15 18:37:30', '2015-06-15 18:37:30', '<strong class="b1"><img src="http://www.isvindia.org/work/seminars/images/seminars.jpg" alt="" width="235" height="343" align="left" /><span class="b1">Interserve </span></strong><span class="txt-normal">works in synergy with the churches and our partners are available for equipping the church to take on the challenges of mission in this generation. It assists the Church in vaious ways:</span>\r\n<table border="0" width="70%" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="9" bgcolor="#93BFF0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF" width="4%">»</td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF">Facilitates one-day mission seminars to create awareness for pastors and local congregations</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD">»</td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD">Provides prayer resources on least-reached people groups in India and overseas to pray more effectively</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF">»</td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF">Facilitates speakers for mission Sundays in Churches to focus on emerging mission challenges</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr bgcolor="#E8EBFD">\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top">»</td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top">Facilitates committed professionals to be sent by home Churches to go across cultures as career missionaries</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF">»</td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF">Facilitates the young and old to go for short-term mission exposure field trips through their Churches.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr bgcolor="#E8EBFD">\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top">»</td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top">Assists in developing customized programs, Bible study on missions etc., for local congregations</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF">»</td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF">Organizes special seminars to learn on sharing our faith with our neighbours at work and at home</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span class="b1">ANTIOCH: Beyond Horizons </span></strong>\r\n\r\n<i>Resources for Wholistic Missions</i>\r\n<span class="b1">Interserve </span><span class="txt-normal">offers seminars which are beyond horizons i.e. transcending traditions, boundaries and cultures to facilitate people for missions. We come alongside the churches to participate in God’s mission.</span>\r\n<table border="0" width="99%" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="9" bgcolor="#93BFF0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF" width="21%"><strong>Wholistic Mission</strong></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Changing Times ...Unchanging Mission! </span></strong>\r\nPresents the challenges of the global mission scenario in today’s changing context</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Towards a Vibrant Sending Church </span></strong>\r\nChallenges the Church to send out missionaries to unreached parts of the world</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Caring for God''s World </span></strong>\r\nEnables Christians to respond biblically to environment crisis</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Mission @ Workplace </span></strong>\r\nPresents the challenges that call for active Christian witness at workplace by tearing the secular-sacred divide</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Business as Mission </span></strong>\r\nGrooms you to be a Christian witness in the market place</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="21%"><strong>Serving Skills</strong></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">The Church and the Marginalized </span></strong>\r\nPresents the challenges of mission to the marginalized segments of society</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Mission to Third Culture Kids </span></strong>\r\nEnables effective ministry with the emerging group of Third culture</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Mission to the Urban Poor </span></strong>\r\nPresents the challenges of mission to the urban poor in the Indian city context</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Mission to Middle Class People Groups </span></strong>\r\nEncourages the Church to reach out to the emerging middle class in India</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="21%"><strong>Leadership</strong></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">''Stand Apart'' – Youth Seminar </span></strong>\r\nHelps the youth in knowing God’s will in their career</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Sharpening Your Interpersonal Skills </span></strong>\r\nEquips people for better interpersonal relations and communication skills</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Leadership in Multicultural Contexts </span></strong>\r\nProvides guidelines for transcending cultures in a multi-cultural team</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Pastoring a Changing World </span></strong>\r\nFacilitates pastors to evolve newer strategies for a more relevant ministry in the emerging contexts</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="21%"><strong>Christian Life</strong></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Fathering and Mothering ''Gen-Next'' </span></strong>\r\nEquips couples to prepare for parenting in today’s tough generation and presents the art of communicating Biblical values to Gen-Next</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Strong Family in a stressed out World </span></strong>\r\nTrains couples to understand current pressures in society and gives instruction on how to balance family-life and work</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Engaging Scripture in Daily Life </span></strong>\r\nTeaches Bible study methods using commentaries and facilitating discussions</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" colspan="2" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EFE0F1"><a href="http://www.isvindia.org/contact/index.html"><u>Contact Us</u> if you would like us to arrange any of the above seminars in your church.</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Envisioning & Equipping Seminars', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'envisioning-equipping-seminars', '', '', '2015-06-15 18:37:30', '2015-06-15 18:37:30', '', 50, 'http://local.wordpress.dev/?page_id=54', 1, 'page', '', 0),
(55, 1, '2015-06-15 18:37:30', '2015-06-15 18:37:30', '<strong class="b1"><img src="http://www.isvindia.org/work/seminars/images/seminars.jpg" alt="" width="235" height="343" align="left" /><span class="b1">Interserve </span></strong><span class="txt-normal">works in synergy with the churches and our partners are available for equipping the church to take on the challenges of mission in this generation. It assists the Church in vaious ways:</span>\r\n<table border="0" width="70%" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="9" bgcolor="#93BFF0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF" width="4%">»</td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF">Facilitates one-day mission seminars to create awareness for pastors and local congregations</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD">»</td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD">Provides prayer resources on least-reached people groups in India and overseas to pray more effectively</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF">»</td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF">Facilitates speakers for mission Sundays in Churches to focus on emerging mission challenges</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr bgcolor="#E8EBFD">\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top">»</td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top">Facilitates committed professionals to be sent by home Churches to go across cultures as career missionaries</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF">»</td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF">Facilitates the young and old to go for short-term mission exposure field trips through their Churches.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr bgcolor="#E8EBFD">\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top">»</td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top">Assists in developing customized programs, Bible study on missions etc., for local congregations</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF">»</td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF">Organizes special seminars to learn on sharing our faith with our neighbours at work and at home</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span class="b1">ANTIOCH: Beyond Horizons </span></strong>\r\n\r\n<i>Resources for Wholistic Missions</i>\r\n<span class="b1">Interserve </span><span class="txt-normal">offers seminars which are beyond horizons i.e. transcending traditions, boundaries and cultures to facilitate people for missions. We come alongside the churches to participate in God’s mission.</span>\r\n<table border="0" width="99%" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="9" bgcolor="#93BFF0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF" width="21%"><strong>Wholistic Mission</strong></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Changing Times ...Unchanging Mission! </span></strong>\r\nPresents the challenges of the global mission scenario in today’s changing context</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Towards a Vibrant Sending Church </span></strong>\r\nChallenges the Church to send out missionaries to unreached parts of the world</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Caring for God''s World </span></strong>\r\nEnables Christians to respond biblically to environment crisis</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Mission @ Workplace </span></strong>\r\nPresents the challenges that call for active Christian witness at workplace by tearing the secular-sacred divide</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Business as Mission </span></strong>\r\nGrooms you to be a Christian witness in the market place</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="21%"><strong>Serving Skills</strong></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">The Church and the Marginalized </span></strong>\r\nPresents the challenges of mission to the marginalized segments of society</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Mission to Third Culture Kids </span></strong>\r\nEnables effective ministry with the emerging group of Third culture</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#E8EBFD"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Mission to the Urban Poor </span></strong>\r\nPresents the challenges of mission to the urban poor in the Indian city context</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF" width="21%"></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#EEF4FF"><span class="b3">»</span> <strong><span class="b1">Mission to Middle Class People Groups </span></strong>\r\nEncourages the Church 