(80, 1, '2015-06-15 19:31:51', '2015-06-15 19:31:51', '<p class="txt-normal">The time has come for tables to be turned around when Indian Christians have to be sent outside India as bearers of the Good News. Globalization has thrown open the doors of opportunities for entrepreneurs and professionals who can be sent as disciple makers.</p>\r\n<p class="txt-normal"><span class="b1"><strong>Interserve </strong>India</span> is poised to be part of the Indian mission movement in this exciting phase of global missions. It has for more than 150 years successfully demonstrated and proven that work and ministry must be integrated. <strong class="b1">Interserve</strong> believes that it is not just few who are called but the whole church that needs to be involved in missions. Its extensive network and partnership with Christian organizations in almost every area of service has enabled it to place hundreds of Christian professionals and entrepreneurs both within and outside India.</p>\r\n<span class="b2">So here is your chance to get involved in mission work by being a part of</span><span class="txt-normal"><strong class="b1"> Interserve</strong> through any of the following programmes:</span>\r\n<table border="0" width="77%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="6" bgcolor="#93BFF0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="17%"><a href="http://www.isvindia.org/get-involved/on-track/index.html">• Join On Track !</a></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="21%"><a href="http://www.isvindia.org/get-involved/partner/index.html">• Become our Partner</a></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="35%"><a href="http://www.isvindia.org/get-involved/macedonian/index.html">• Unite with us on a Macedonian Call</a></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" bgcolor="#E8EBFD" width="27%"><a href="http://www.isvindia.org/get-involved/friend/index.html">• Be a Friend of Interserve</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Get Involved', '',