(83, 1, '2015-06-15 19:33:09', '2015-06-15 19:33:09', '<p class="txt-normal"><span class="b3">OnTrack!</span> is a volunteer mission exposure program at <strong class="b1">Interserve</strong> designed for individuals and teams from local churches in cross cultural contexts in India and beyond. On Track has both  short-term (1to 6 mths) and long-term (1 to 2 yrs) programmes through which we help Christians to serve the Lord in a field of their interest. <span class="b1"><strong>Interserve</strong>’s</span> extensive network and partnership with Christian organizations in almost every area of service makes it the best choice for short term enthusiasts.</p>\r\n<span class="b3">OnTrack!</span><span class="txt-normal"> consists of four different tracks. Get ready for a life-transforming experience, a time of close communion with God and service to His people.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<table border="0" width="99%" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="9" bgcolor="#93BFF0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" bgcolor="#EEF4FF" width="23%">» <strong>Track 1 – 18+</strong></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" bgcolor="#EEF4FF" width="77%"><span class="b2">18+</span> is for students who want to use their vacations to serve the Lord after your 12th or your degree or maybe your summer vacations. All you need is a minimum of 2 weeks to spare. Based on your interests and talents, we will find just the right place for you.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" bgcolor="#E8EBFD">» <strong>Track 2 – ComeAway</strong></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" bgcolor="#E8EBFD"><span class="b2">ComeAway</span> is tailor-made for working professionals who want to take time off their work and serve the Lord for a specified period of time. Exposure can be arranged in the area of your expertise or in any other area of interest. Interserve has partnerships with Christian organizations across the spectrum to help you find the right placement.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="b1" bgcolor="#EEF4FF">» <strong>Track 3 – Cliqued</strong></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal" bgcolor="#EEF4FF"><span class="b2">Cliqued</span> is for group exposure. It is for church groups or groups from any Christian organization who want to send their members on a group exposure trip. Working and travelling as a team provides invaluable times of fellowship and character building. It also provides a wonderful time of service and a team can work better on projects.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr bgcolor="#E8EBFD">\r\n<td class="b1">» <strong>Track 4 – Rejuvenate</strong></td>\r\n<td class="txt-normal"><span class="b2">Rejuvenate</span> is ideal for Christians who have retired from service and want to use part of their retired life to serve the Lord and His people. Interserve provides excellent member care when you are in the field and will place you right where you belong and enjoy the presence of God through service and fellowship.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<table border="0" width="45%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="9" bgcolor="#93BFF0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr bgcolor="#E8EBFD">\r\n<td class="txt-normal" bgcolor="#EFE0F1" width="95%"><span class="b1">»</span> <a href="http://www.isvindia.org/contact/index.html">If interested in volunteering, <u>Contact Us</u> for further information.</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Join On Track!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'join-on-track', '', '', '2015-06-15 19:33:35', '2015-06-15 19:33:35', '', 80, 'http://local.wordpress.dev/?page_id=83', 10, 'page', '', 0),
