(96, 1, '2015-06-15 19:38:39', '2015-06-15 19:38:39', '<p class="txt-normal">You may be placed anywhere in the world, but may want to support the work of God through<span class="b1"> <strong>Interserve</strong></span><strong>.</strong> Here is an opportunity for you to support<span class="b1"><strong>Interserve</strong> </span><span class="b2">Partners</span> in Asia / Arab World. You can support the work of <strong class="b2">Interserve </strong>and its workers through prayer and financial support individually or in groups. <strong> <span class="b1">Interserve</span></strong><span class="b2"> Partners</span> are involved in varied fields of community development and are sustained by the freewill offerings of children of God globally.</p>\r\n<span class="txt-normal">Your support could help our </span><span class="b2">Partners</span><span class="txt-normal"> in the field to work more effectively without the added burden of continual financial constraints. It would also provide you a wonderful way to use your money to transform the world with the gospel of Jesus Christ.\r\nTake a step and forward and support this great cause.</span>\r\n<table border="0" width="64%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="9" bgcolor="#93BFF0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr bgcolor="#E8EBFD">\r\n<td class="txt-normal" bgcolor="#EFE0F1" width="95%"><span class="b1">» </span><a href="http://www.isvindia.org/contact/index.html"><u>Contact Us</u> to learn more about how you can support us and become a friend of Interserve</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Be a Friend of Interserve', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'be-a-friend-of-interserve', '', '', '2015-06-15 19:38:58', '2015-06-15 19:38:58', '', 80, 'http://local.wordpress.dev/?page_id=96', 40, 'page', '', 0),
